Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敏捷又强大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fleet and forceful
