Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he becomes weak
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的水母啊  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumpin' jellyfish, Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在破坏防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's destroying the shield
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, Barnacle Boy
