Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.86,0:02:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  开门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, open up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反光怪发现我们的秘密实验室了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reflecto has found our secret lab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正的美人鱼战士会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would the real Mermaid Man do?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要不然就自个去问人家好不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask him yourself?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说详细点  你这卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elaborate, you vile fiend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他跟企鹅男孩就住在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He and Barnacle Boy live in
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,城对面的养老院里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the retirement home on the other side of town
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们肯定在执行卧底工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They must be working undercover
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  现在求你们别来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now please leave me alone
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.60,0:03:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩重新合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy, reunite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1087,738)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(939,366)}辍学率飙升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(885,762)}全球海洋变暖
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.15,0:03:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听说美人鱼战士在为重要任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know Mermaid Man is working undercover
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,执行卧底工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on an important case
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们可以看一下他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but do you think we could see him?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卧底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Undercover?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我来查看一下他们能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I'll see if they can
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从忙碌日程当中抽空来看你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take time from their busy schedule to see you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了  他们就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here they are, right over there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽量不要太刺激到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try not to surprise them
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你相信不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can you believe it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩本人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy in the flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:12.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(733,732)}塔塔酱
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些人谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are those guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是来修电视的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are they here to fix the TV?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们从前还是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we used to be
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在我们退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but now we're retired
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你们不能退休
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you can't retire
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有邪恶正在落脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's evil afoot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What evil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要忘记还有邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget there's evil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是说还有邪恶正在落脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I said was there's evil afoot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you please stop saying that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgrace
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可惜他们老了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too bad they're old
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么意思  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老人家最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old people are the greatest
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们充满着智慧与经验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're full of wisdom and experience
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个世界需要美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The world needs Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某个人  某个地方有了危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone, somewhere is in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不到美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩不再退休
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I won't rest until Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我决不罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are out of retirement
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty lights
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1123,640)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往肉糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the meatloaf
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往西兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the broccoli
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.29,0:05:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要给我的年轻孩子多打点西兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make sure you give extra broccoli to my young ward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位孩子很需要维生素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boy needs his vitamins
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, son
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往餐桌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the table--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,away
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点  不要乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful, don't run
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,修电视的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes the TV repairman
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想从我们这要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want from us?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let me look at you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持警惕  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay alert, Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他另有目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's up to something
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you call --
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别叫我男孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you stop calling me boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们记不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you remember
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亚特兰蒂斯食物供给不足的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the time the food supply in Atlantis was running low?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是你们发明了一把射线枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you invented a ray gun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这枪能让东西放大到原本大小的六倍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that made things grow six times their size
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们用这枪射海草园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to shoot at the kelp gardens
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶的射线恶魔突然袭击  把枪掳走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the evil man ray swoops down and swipes the gun away
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并射向了所有海藻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and shoots all the algae
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后他附在海底穹顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he gloms onto the undersea dome
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他开始吸玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he starts sucking on the glass
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想表达什么  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your point, kid?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是史上最棒的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys are the greatest heroes of all time
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得你们应该不再退休
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I think you should come out of retirement
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  你们这些恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up, you villains
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想吃我的肉糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to eat my meatloaf
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you don't get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就用我身上的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then by the power invested in me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宣布你们结为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I now pronounce you man and wife
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is going on in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以亲新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may kiss the bride
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让我们的英雄重新合为一体了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you reunite our heroes?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm married
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞  飞  飞高高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, up and away
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞  飞  飞高高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, up and away
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个包真是又大又重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This purse is so big and heavy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许动  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把包抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是来救我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you here to rescue little old me?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pipe down
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会吵醒美人鱼战士的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to wake Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦他被吵醒就会出岔子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he's awry when his nap is disturbed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever alert
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士练成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man has trained himself
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睁眼睡觉的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to sleep with his eye open
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦人精  离他远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Confounded, get away from him
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别喊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop shouting
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm napping
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我喊的  你这老不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not me, you old coot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm over here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This better be good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个肯定能让你们高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This will cheer you up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.81,0:08:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们差不多已经
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're almost done
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重新漆完了你们的无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,painting your invisible boat mobile
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来应该无影的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be invisible
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的休闲时光必须结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to end our life of leisure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候不再退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to come out of retirement
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶正在落脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's evil afoot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道意味着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doughnuts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,念咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say the oath
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.64,0:09:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩  合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy, unite
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朝他扔水弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Throw a water ball at him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water balls
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water balls
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海鳗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mumbling morays
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没用  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not working, Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.03,0:09:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在吸收水弹  就像个邪恶海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's absorbing it like some kind of evil sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狗刨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dog paddle away
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是汹涌漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the raging whirlpool
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fiends
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们还很享受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're actually enjoying it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what, Mermaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need help
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底生物  联合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea creatures, unite
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海洋生物好像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The creatures of the deep seemed to
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不再光芒万丈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have lost some of their luster
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底生物  进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea creatures, attack
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掐我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinch me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must be dreaming
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任务完成了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉自己年轻了五岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel five years younger
