Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.57,0:12:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tomatoes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包  按顺序摆好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bun in that order
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼喊强尼做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One crying johnny up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十二份加小麦面包的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twelve Krabby Patties on wheat buns
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.91,0:12:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包肉饼番茄酱番茄面包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bun, patty, ketchup, tomato, bun
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一打呼喊农场奶牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One dozen crying cows on the farm
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  农夫布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Farmer Brown
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能服务你让我好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's been a thrill serving you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能加点盐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get some extra salt?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以去看一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you check?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.30,0:13:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我猜猜  小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, Tiny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要一小份沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A small salad?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份双层三重全牛豪华堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take a Double Triple Bossy Deluxe
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤面包当底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a raft
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四轮驱动巨无霸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,four-by-four, animal-style
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多加带状疱疹  再摇一摇挤一挤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,extra shingles with a shimmy and a squeeze
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少加润滑油  让它哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,light axle grease, make it cry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烧了它  让它在水里游
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,burn it and let it swim
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这是卖饭的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We serve food here, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经做好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it already, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听说你很会做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hear talk you make a mean Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听说你很挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hear talk you're kind of picky
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王  觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Bubble Bass, what do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is pretty good
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only one thing--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘加腌椰菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot the pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.13,0:14:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这还最好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The best there is?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lose
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是腌椰菜本来应该就在这的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the pickles should be right where they always are
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我记得我放了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I put them on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are those pickles?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们得退我两块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe you owe me two bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your guarantee
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(689,722)}退款保证
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能再商量下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, can we talk about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要卫生间代币折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a discount on restroom tokens?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.96,0:14:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:14:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来杯免费的水怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a free glass of water?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一打免费的水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dozen free glasses of water
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还加了冰块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll even put ice in it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两块钱  两块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two dollars, two dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
