Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I put pickles on that Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那两块钱从你工资里面扣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That two bucks is coming out of your paycheck
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to work
