Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got orders waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a Krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  这回我肯定不会搞砸
