Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the work
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本不会把肉饼放面包上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't put a patty on a bun
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再加上生菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with lettuce
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.07,0:20:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.40,0:20:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,onions
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tomatoes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.19,0:20:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ketchup
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.57,0:20:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mustard
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有顶上的面包  按顺序摆好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and top bun together in that order
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.74,0:20:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.89,0:20:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说海绵宝宝回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hear SquarePants is back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为我把你赶出这座城了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I ran you out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where I belong
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我来份老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me the regular
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别忘了加腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't forget the pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是没有腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still no pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又输了  废物宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You failed again, SpongeBob-loser-pants
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.22,0:22:12.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一直都把腌椰菜藏在舌头底下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:12.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's been hiding the pickles under his tongue the whole time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里头还有上次的腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there's the pickle from last time, too
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我的车钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there's my car keys
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我该溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there's my ride
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.28,0:22:27.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为我们的大厨海绵宝宝回归欢呼三声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for the return
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of our Mr. Fry Cook, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.99,0:22:28.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:28.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hip-hip--
