Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为在我不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And three cheers for the fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.12,0:22:40.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我代班的煎炸厨师章鱼哥欢呼三声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:40.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who took my place while I was gone, Squidward
